      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria:

        Women, 50 year or more Menopausal women Breast cancer Macroscopic tumor size of 10 mm or
        less (measured during operation) No palpable axillary node ( N0)

        Exclusion criteria:

        Previous cancer history life expectancy &lt; 10 years Metastasis
      </textblock>
